FRESH light is expected to be shed on the industrial espionage battle between General Motors and Volkswagen later today when criminal investigators are due to issue their first formal statement since they started the search for evidence in late April.
The Darmstadt state prosecutor s office which took up the investigation at GM s request after Mr Jose Ignacio Lopez de Arriortua defected from GM to VW in March said its statement would cover progress so far.
