It was unlikely that statements would be issued immediately on any possible evidence uncovered he said.
Mr Nauth added that as well as interrogating junior VW employees who allegedly fed Opel data into the VW data base the prosecutor in charge of the case Ms Dorothea Holland had also questioned Mr Carl Hahn former VW chairman.
Mr Lopez and his associates had not yet been interviewed.
We assume the investigating authorities do not take such action without having strong reasons to do so.
